    "skin": null,
    "faith": null,
    "description": "Spurt is a russet-colored kobold who collects critters and has several on her person, including a skunk in a wooden cage, several wasps in a bag, and centipedes in a basket. Although she can aggravate enemies by releasing these critters, she has no control over their behavior."
